content:
## JavaScript API

To access the JavaScript API documentation, please first build the design system app using:

```sh
npm run doc
```

Then, start the production web server:

```sh
bin/otrs.WebServer.pl
```

Finally, open the following URL in your browser:
[http://localhost:8080/dist/api/index.html](http://localhost:8080/dist/api/index.html)

You can find specific module documentation in the left sidebar.
